Loadout Builder
- Checkbox to select an item for a loadout
- Selected items stay pinned to the top

Loot Guide
- Bottom pane shows the loot guide
- Left pane shows a tree of items that should be collected to maintain the loadout
- Right pane shows items that can be recycled into items that should be collected to maintain the loadout

Improve mobile experience
- Reduce size of header, inline link to data repo
- Make max width smaller for name in portrait mode

