- Pipeline outputs structured data, defer flattening rows to renderRow
- Pipeline just focuses on filtering and 
  - Reducing the size of data to load for faster start time
  - Restructuring data
  - Building any indices that are needed (idToName, trees)
- Renderer handles
  - Flattening the structure
  - Substituting names for IDs
  - Formatting multi-line text as either a comma-separate list or a   
    multi-line row

